rows.label: bf06330100_0060
rows.name: (I've seen one like it before, in old Iira.)

rows.label: bf06330100_0070
rows.name: (It certainly seems like they want us gone for good...)

rows.label: bf06330100_0090
rows.name:
(If we cranked up the output and
really focused it...)

rows.label: bf06330100_0110
rows.name:
If the people here really are the
descendants of the Iirans...

rows.label: bf06330100_0120
rows.name: then I have a message for them that I must pass on.

rows.label: bf06330100_0130
rows.name: (In that case, I'll leave it to you.)

rows.label: bf06330100_0160
rows.name:
I apologize, Heavenly Grail.
I bear no direct grudge against you.

rows.label: bf06330100_0170
rows.name:
However... For the sake of this world...
You must be destroyed where you stand.

rows.label: bf06330100_0180
rows.name:
Is that truly your desire,
Your Majesty?

rows.label: bf06330100_0190
rows.name: That should have been your wish as well,

rows.label: bf06330100_0200
rows.name:
from that day when you disappeared 
from history with the hero Adel...

rows.label: bf06330100_0270
rows.name:
A weapon built long ago
That uses Genbu's ether energy.

rows.label: bf06330100_0280
rows.name: To think it was properly restored...

rows.label: bf06330100_0290
rows.name: My old man... He's gonna use it to kill Homura!

rows.label: bf06330100_0300
rows.name:
No matter how strong she is,
there'd be no coming back from that!
